311
00:18:24,689 --> 00:18:26,978
Uh, as lâmpadas, as íris.

312
00:18:27,002 --> 00:18:28,876
[Mulher] Alguns narcisos também?

313
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:30,706
- Ah, sim.
