394
00:23:58,989 --> 00:23:59,989
[Araz] Delphinium?

395
00:24:04,201 --> 00:24:05,799
[Falando persa]

396
00:24:05,823 --> 00:24:08,619
[Araz] Nunca ouvi esse.
